      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">7/4/92 ¶ After receiving your kind letter this morning, ¶ Letter not found. ¶  ¶ dear Commandeur Archer, I wrote and sent a letter to the Under Secretary, ¶ Letter not found.A deputation from the Roya...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">92.04.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Henry Archer</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">2/137/17, Archer papers, University of Melbourne Archives.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7/4/92</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">After receiving your kind letter this morning,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dear Commandeur Archer, I wrote and sent a letter to the Under Secretary,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>A deputation from the Royal Society of Victoria met the Chief<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Secretary on 7 April,</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">and strongly urged</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">that the sum of money to b</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>set aside for th</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Government Botanist's department should b</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e i</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ncreas</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">d</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">from £1200 to £1500 a year. Mr</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">M'L</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ean</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>r</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ma</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">r</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ked that the matter</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>h</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ad</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">been</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">carefully consider</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">d by the Cabinet b</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">for</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>t</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">he<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">retrenchment was agreed upon; but in view of</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">the strong representations made by the society</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">h</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>would again bring the matter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">u</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">nd</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">r the</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">notice of his colleagues</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">8 April 1892, p. 4</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pointing out, that I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">recognize</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">gratefully</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>the kind efforts made by the science-Societies and particularly the Deputation on behalf of my Department, but that I would keep the collections<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">safe</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">under</hi>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">utilisation</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for the £400 left me as working expenses; but that I should feel most thankful if young<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">French</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles H. French.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>could<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">remain</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with me at the additional expense of £128<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>-. -.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>annually</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I was of course<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">not really</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">hostile</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to the movement on my behalf, but I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">was</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">afraid</hi>
               </seg>, it was inopportune, as Mr M’Lean and his Colleagues<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>time is<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>just now taken up by the elections extra,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>— as the new estimates are only framed in May or June, and as I was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">frighten</hi>
               </seg>,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>frightened?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">discussions</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by the Deputation before<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Reporte</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">rs</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>might lead to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">new expressions</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">against</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Ministry also possible<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>possibly?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to public suggestion too rashly made. Perhaps you like to send this letter for perusal to our friend Prof Spencer.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Baldwin Spencer.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
